# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:（投資、賭博等）虧本之後，即刻賣出或停止投入，以減少更多損失（量詞：次）
eng:to cut losses; to stop a loss
<eg>
yue:佢買咗隻股票跌得好勁，所以即刻止蝕。 (keoi5 maai5 zo2 zek6 gu3 piu3 dat1 de2 hou2 ging6, so2 jik6 zai6 zai2 sik6.)
eng:He bought a stock that fell sharply, so he immediately cut his losses.

<eg>
yue:唔好再輸啦，快啲止蝕啦！ (m4 hou2 zoi6 syu1 laa1, faai3 dai1 zai2 sik6 laa1!)
eng:Stop losing more, cut your losses quickly! [end of text]


